<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Delete a Book</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="logo.jpg">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fff8f0;
        }

        .delete-page {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .left-section {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #f4f0e1;
            color: #3e3e3e;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            box-shadow: 4px 0 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .left-section h2 {
            color: #2d2d2d;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .left-section p {
            color: #3e3e3e;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .right-section {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: -4px 0 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .right-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2d2d2d;
        }

        form {
            width: 80%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        form label {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #3e3e3e;
        }

        form input {
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        form button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #d4a85a;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        form button:hover {
            background-color: #c78e3f;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="delete-page">
        <div class="left-section">
            <h2>Welcome to IntoLibrary!</h2>
            <p>If you no longer wish to keep a book in your collection, you can easily delete it. Just enter the book name below and confirm the deletion.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="right-section">
            <h2>Delete a Book</h2>
            <form action="/libdelete" method="POST">
                <label for="_id">Book Unique ID:</label>
                <input type="text" id="_id" name="_id" required>
            
                <button type="submit">Delete Book</button>
            </form>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
